## 02_故事引擎事件条_紧凑仪表盘

### 查找正则

```regex
/^\s*-\s*(事件[^:：\n]+)[:：]\s*(.*?)(?:\s*(\(\d{1,3}%\)))?\s*$/gm
```

### 替换内容

```html
<div class="se-event-card"><div class="se-event-top"><span class="se-event-name">$1</span><span class="se-event-rate">$3</span></div><div class="se-event-text">$2</div></div>
```

